title: Hotel Easy Booker for Android v1.2.4
description:
Free hotel finder application for searching and booking over 210 000 hotels worldwide. No booking fees. 
You can search hotels also near your current location. Your location will be determined either by GPS or wireless networks. It is recommended to use wireless networks if there is no GPS signal. 


Features:
- Search over 210 000 hotels
- Search hotels near your current location
- Browse hotel photos
- View hotel location on map
- Sort search results by popularity, price, stars, guest rating
- Install app to SD card
- Hotel deals
